    <p>After 10 years, Fen Nena realized that he had to increase the variety of products in his store. Knowing this, he decided to sell food he cooked by himself. Since then, his store had been in frenzy. Many people have been visiting his store and buying his products and food. With his great knowledge of economics and marketing, he was able to expand his market to different areas in the country. Examples are Valenzuela, Pasig, Quezon, Marikina and Malabon.</p> 
    <p>After another 10 years, Fen Nena now has a family of 5. Since he already grew old, he knows that he would hand the business down to his eldest son again. But because of his eldest son's incompetence, he has to make sure that the business would grow at a maximum pace before he retires.</p>
    <br><br><br><br><br><br>
